text: mariyu memu musa koraku (sinayi kondapai) muppai ratrula (gaduvu) nirnayincamu. Taruvata padi (ratrulu) podigincamu. I vidhanga atani prabhuvu nirnayincina nalabhai ratrula guduva purtayyindi. Musa tana sodarudagu harun to annadu: "Nivu na jati prajalalo naku pratinithyam vahincu mariyu sanskaranaku patu padu mariyu aracakalu cesevari marganni anusarincaku
